{"tid":1002953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老母叫我俾家用","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T09:32:38.000Z","uid":190585,"like":426,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1ba7f9c052180dad5599205f05c7b34336c0e3","tid":1002953,"uid":190585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"我個人認為有得俾咪俾，冇都冇辨法。老母養左我咁耐，等佢每個月有多幾千蚊使都不為過。<br />\n<br />\n之但係我啱啱畢業又未搵到工，去邊度俾錢你？我都係part time啱啱夠兩餐。又話我自私，不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾日躁躁地咁開片話: 鬼佬啲老豆老母都唔會問仔女攞家用啦。我老母就屌我話人地係鬼佬，你係唔係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我又冇話唔俾，你係咁jer住我搞到好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。而家搞到好似啲錢仲緊要過自己個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 老母除左有俾飽飯我食同交學費之後，淨係識日日屌鳩我。成日講人地個仔點點點，你又睇唔睇到人地老豆老母點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7aa71eef60530f960a15763ae974db9129faf5","tid":1002953,"uid":190585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fb1989df34ba0bac6ff7631d3a8348b722bc10","tid":1002953,"uid":190585,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"點撚樣答佢好？"},{"pid":"6776338efb9a415e175f9e53c0f838e2d36d42d2","tid":1002953,"uid":94828,"like":26,"dislike":68,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"乖乖地交 <br />\n生生性性下世投胎做鬼佬"},{"pid":"71a78fbe8cbceafe4daab62e277f8caae8daf0a7","tid":1002953,"uid":190585,"like":120,"dislike":4,"score":116,"quote":{"pid":"6776338efb9a415e175f9e53c0f838e2d36d42d2","tid":1002953,"uid":94828,"like":26,"dislike":68,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"乖乖地交 <br />\n生生性性下世投胎做鬼佬"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"根本唔係鬼唔鬼佬嘅問題 我老母都唔講道理<img src=\"/assets/face